arStrings.szText:
Casting {c_important}Landslide{/c} causes tectonic spikes to continue to deal {c_random}[(Owner.Weapon_Damage_Min_Total + Owner.Weapon_Damage_Delta_Total) * Affix_Value_1]{/c} damage over {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0"]{/c} seconds.

Summoning {c_important}Landslide{/c} pillars in tectonic spikes has a {c_random}[Affix_Value_2 * 100|%|]{/c} chance to causes extra {c_important}Landslide{/c} pillars to spawn in the spikes.
